ihkg.com/thread/1889094/page/1</a><br />\n黨鐵關閉元朗站，一個月比一個月遲<br />\n係咪睇撚死我地？<br />\n<br />\n唔得閒cap圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498835-20191220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498835-20191220.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=3c09e034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498835-20191220.htm&h=f071c364\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498835-20191220.htm</a><br />\n港鐵：因應公眾活動 西鐵綫元朗站明午<span style=\"color: red;\">1時</span>起暫時關閉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2019-12-20 </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503833-20200120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503833-20200120.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=27da6221\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503833-20200120.htm&h=c2ed33a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503833-20200120.htm</a><br />\n港鐵明午<span style=\"color: red;\">3時</span>起關西鐵元朗站 稱基於詳細風險評估<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020-01-20 </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509793-20200220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509793-20200220.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=b787aaf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509793-20200220.htm&h=2fd57bdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509793-20200220.htm</a><br />\n港鐵宣布元朗站明天下午<span style=\"color: red;\">5時</span>起暫時關閉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020-02-20 </span>"},{"pid":"073df4aa15e2558178cd297c1a78a491932a1dbf","tid":1876460,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"搵區議員幫手監察食環跟進違規藍店嘛"},{"pid":"f61fd85cccf79064cb7b24056df0293c6c270149","tid":1876460,"uid":36612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}